content.contentDesc:
W: Where were you yesterday afternoon, Fred?

M: Do you mean during basketball practice, Mary?

W: Yes. What happened to you?

M: I had to go to the doctor's again. Was Mr. Smith angry? I forgot to tell him I was not going to take part in it.

W: Well, he wasn't very happy about it.

M: How was the practice?

W: Not very good. Everybody seemed tired. And Tom got hurt.

M: Was he hurt badly?

W: No. He hurt his arm a little. He's OK today. And of course, Charles can't play because of his leg.

M: Who played instead of Charles?

W: Ray did. He's not very good.

M: What about Carl? He's fast.

W: Yes, but he's short. Well, you've got to be there this afternoon. Four o'clock as usual.

M: I know. I'll be there then.

subContents.content: What did Fred do yesterday afternoon?

options.option: He went to the doctor.

subContents.content: What time will the basketball practice begin this afternoon?

analysisList.text:
第一空是推理判断题。题干中出现：So he drove to him and asked，由ask可以推出后半句应该是个问句，纵观五个选项，只有D是where引导的特殊疑问句。

因此，正确答案是D。

第二空是推理判断题。根据前文的提问：Where are you going, sir?你去哪里先生？回答应该是去个地方，纵观五个选项，只有A是回答地方。

因此，正确答案是A。

第三空是细节理解题。题干中司机对乘客说：You should pay me fifteen dollars。乘客需要付15美元。乘客的反应是：What? 什么？结合句意，乘客应该是对这15美元的价格感到吃惊，选项C符合。

因此，正确答案是C。

第四空是推理判断题。提干中提到：I took a taxi from the railway station to this hotel and I only gave the driver thirteen dollars.上周乘客从车站到酒店坐出租车只花了13美元，结合句意，说明该乘客知道从车站到酒店的价格，选项E符合。

因此，正确答案是E。

subContents.content:
It was a cold night. The taxi driver didn't take even one passenger all day. When he went by the railway station, he saw a young man coming out with two bags in his hands. So he drove to him and asked, "__$$__"

"__$$__" the young man answered. When the taxi driver heard this, he didn't feel happy any more. The young man would give him only three dollars because the hotel was near the railway station, but suddenly, he had an idea. He took the young man through many streets of the big city.

After a long time, they arrived at the hotel. "Here we are! You should pay me fifteen dollars, please," the taxi driver said to the young man." What? __$$__ Do you think I'm a fool? Only last week, I took a taxi from the railway station to this hotel and I only gave the driver thirteen dollars. __$$__"

options.option: I know how much I have to pay for the trip.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是短文结构顺序的理解。根据题干短文内容可知要去参加一个生日晚会首先要“give invitations to their friends.”，然后是朋友要接受邀请，接着“People usually take a birthday present to a birthday party.”，然后朋友们一起在生日聚会上很开心，最后聚会结束后大部分人会写一封感谢信或者打电话道谢。结合选项意思，可以进行排序。

因此，正确答案是5,2,4,1,3。

subContents.content:
Invitations (邀请)

Invitations are important. In the west, people often give invitations to their friends. Most invitations are for dinner or a birthday party. When people accept (接受) an invitation to a dinner or party, they usually ask what they can bring. They often take flowers, chocolates, or other presents. People usually take a birthday present to a birthday party. After a dinner or birthday party , most people telephone the host (主人) to say "thank you". Some people write a short thank-you note or send an e-mail to the host.

Mary想邀请James参加生日晚会，请将以下各项活动按正确的顺序排列，把序号填入相应的横线上。

options.option: Mary and James enjoy the party together.
Mary invites her friend James to her birthday party.

analysisList.text: I am HanHan. I went to Hainan on holiday last summer. I said goodbye to my parents at the airport in Zhengzhou and flew to Haikou. I stayed with my aunt, Lili. She had a boat and we wanted to go sailing! We have a lovely time sailing! One morning I decided to stand on the side of the boat. Suddenly, I fell off into the sea. I didn’t know how to swim and I began to shout. Then, I felt something push me nearer to the boat. It was a dolphin and he was trying to help me! My aunt heard me shout and pull me back on the boat. I have now learnt to swim and been good at swimming. I will always love dolphins!

Dave's uncle works on a farm in America. He likes swimming, too. He wants to work in Hangzhou. (3) 但是他不会说汉语。

因此，正确答案是They are from America。

因此，正确答案是She likes painting and playing chess。

description: 你将有60秒钟的时间阅读屏幕上的短文，并作朗读准备。在听到“开始录音”的信号后，请在90秒钟内朗读短文一遍。

subContents.content:
I'm worried about my friend Jolin. She wants to be a model and she's thin, but she thinks she's fat. She's always on a diet. She's getting too thin. But whenever I talk to her about this, she gets angry. How can I help her?

I have to share a room with my seven-year old sister, and she's driving me mad! She has a habit of playing the piano when I'm studying, and she always takes my things without telling me. I try to keep the room tidy, but she always makes a mess. I love my sister, but sometimes she's so annoying! What should I do?

description: 请你根据所给的情景与提示扮演角色，进行提问或回答4个问题。在完成每个问题之前，你有5秒钟左右的准备时间，按照提示在规定时间内录音。角色: Han Fang, Michael。情景: Han Fang询问Michael的兴趣爱好。提示: Michael通常在网上读新闻，看视频还有和同学聊天等。你将扮演Han Fang的角色。
